rows.label: qst701704_msg0001
rows.name: The Silent Specter, eh? I see.

rows.label: qst701704_msg0003
rows.name:
I've got my hands fair full with looking
after my partner. I don't have time to
care about other goings-on.

rows.label: qst701704_msg0004
rows.name:
From what I know, you won't find
normal folks who know anything about
who you're looking for, though.
